{"tid":131830,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"六月東歐遊跪求建議","createTime":"2017-02-23T10:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T13:38:26.000Z","uid":45044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"763adfa4a7a606181ed89375f80b678ffb03b4c4","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"華沙<br />\n克拉科夫<br />\n波羅的海<br />\n芬蘭<br />\n聖彼得堡<br />\n<br />\n見到平機票買左1/6華沙 27/6聖彼得堡走<br />\n好似唔洗咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇以上地方day trip推薦？特別係波羅的海三國 d人話首都一日行晒 我仲要留四五日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db24875ec4efd808e1dc05ba5462062105c1ed1","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"我上年又係廿六日<br />\n<br />\n不過我落埋去烏克蘭，摩爾多瓦成個禮拜。<br />\n<br />\n另外俄仔飛地八日。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭同俄仔飛地都係第二次去，所以有啲景唔洗再去多次。<br />\n<br />\n要玩睇埋白俄免簽實施未，實施咗嘅話，可以玩陸路，立陶宛入境，烏克蘭或波蘭出境。<br />\n<br />\n除咗首都仲有好多城市玩。"},{"pid":"32955c23b9f6f620d62f9882d0185cf514cdf2c4","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上年又係廿六日<br />\n<br />\n不過我落埋去烏克蘭，摩爾多瓦成個禮拜。<br />\n<br />\n另外俄仔飛地八日。<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭同俄仔飛地都係第二次去，所以有啲景唔洗再去多次。<br />\n<br />\n要玩睇埋白俄免簽實施未，實施咗嘅話，可以玩陸路，立陶宛入境，烏克蘭或波蘭出境。<br />\n<br />\n除咗首都仲有好多城市玩。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9152b1f857fd08c466349e0ff3698275d678bf","tid":131830,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"上年去咗華莎同克拉科夫<br />\n華莎去咗2日 無咩好玩 <br />\n真係唔駛留太耐<br />\n<br />\n克拉科夫去咗3日<br />\n去睇鹽礦1日<br />\n(建議跟local tour <br />\n因為自己散買平唔得幾多)<br />\n去集中營1日好正"},{"pid":"e9bbe0a1eeaa7f31507d0189035caad106e7d5e6","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！"},{"pid":"bb754455e721c47725e318caaa6c2f80094221b0","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉屌 今次plan行程plan到成pat屎咁 想去gdansk nida近海d城市都去唔到 唯有下次先去"},{"pid":"c03131545c843f96da5d113b51777b9f9e6f78cd","tid":131830,"uid":58081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"點平法？<br />\n之前望華沙單程都幾貴<br />\n最後轉左去莫斯科"},{"pid":"20ebbb42b7aaa07e3de906bec10135c5de43e5a0","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點平法？<br />\n之前望華沙單程都幾貴<br />\n最後轉左去莫斯科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$32xx<br />\n不過Aeroflot 莫斯科轉機有d淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86387d5b0a1104f4766e51a3fe4508f7225090b6","tid":131830,"uid":4428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:20:59.000Z","msg":"LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐"},{"pid":"dfa844054046d022c652c45dd0fb6a7271cebf21","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:22:55.000Z","msg":"唔記得講，三國+聖彼德堡係前年去！<br />\n<br />\n唔係同一年，所以你得廿六日唔算好多，聖彼得堡都可以四，五日。<br />\n<br />\n上年廿六日，坐芬航落奧斯陸，赫爾辛基轉機，即晚坐壞人航空落 Gdansk。<br />\n<br />\n由波蘭玩起，最後由摩爾多瓦飛返 Helsinki 返香港"},{"pid":"3cd5178d87e67f66f289b24908086486cb82b6cc","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉屌 今次plan行程plan到成pat屎咁 想去gdansk nida近海d城市都去唔到 唯有下次先去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你中間乜都未 book 嘅話都可以改啦，除非酒店，中間交通 book 晒。"},{"pid":"c0f5540f16a0e5e92711a761b8e9f396680923a1","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間"},{"pid":"67d72bb752a21d6ee9c887828b9950c466c2dd22","tid":131830,"uid":58081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點平法？<br />\n之前望華沙單程都幾貴<br />\n最後轉左去莫斯科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$32xx<br />\n不過Aeroflot 莫斯科轉機有d淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁差唔多啦<br />\n俄羅斯來回都係3000左右"},{"pid":"8992645aeb220a06474d0edc5ab4f99e90bc0001","tid":131830,"uid":58081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間</blockquote><br />\n我早你地少少，5了月尾<br />\n到時可以約個地方食飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cadbaac7b01c535609a6697d1c9451c83c0d6b","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點平法？<br />\n之前望華沙單程都幾貴<br />\n最後轉左去莫斯科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$32xx<br />\n不過Aeroflot 莫斯科轉機有d淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵啦，咁平。<br />\n<br />\n有幾耐時間轉機先？<br />\n<br />\n我查過我計劃中嘅 trip 要轉內陸機，佢夠膽得個半鐘。<br />\n<br />\n要 passport control 入境要拎行李，再 check in 寄行李，第一程 delay 就玩完！"},{"pid":"8a31667476f9facb156108ec86621fed863ec51b","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間</blockquote><br />\n我早你地少少，5了月尾<br />\n到時可以約個地方食飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啊 獨遊撚最鐘意識朋友<br />\n不過我1/6先飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fffc9d6347a947721705378c8343ef8bc760c94","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早你一個月，不過齋去俄仔"},{"pid":"f93f54b4b5e6cf411048c4c643f5f4704432fd2f","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點平法？<br />\n之前望華沙單程都幾貴<br />\n最後轉左去莫斯科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$32xx<br />\n不過Aeroflot 莫斯科轉機有d淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵啦，咁平。<br />\n<br />\n有幾耐時間轉機先？<br />\n<br />\n我查過我計劃中嘅 trip 要轉內陸機，佢夠膽得個半鐘。<br />\n<br />\n要 passport control 入境要拎行李，再 check in 寄行李，第一程 delay 就玩完！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係個半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係國際機<br />\n由於真係太平 我已經做好要delay嘅心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b07669f9791a84e65126c33f6dbbb0800156f42","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點平法？<br />\n之前望華沙單程都幾貴<br />\n最後轉左去莫斯科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$32xx<br />\n不過Aeroflot 莫斯科轉機有d淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抵啦，咁平。<br />\n<br />\n有幾耐時間轉機先？<br />\n<br />\n我查過我計劃中嘅 trip 要轉內陸機，佢夠膽得個半鐘。<br />\n<br />\n要 passport control 入境要拎行李，再 check in 寄行李，第一程 delay 就玩完！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係個半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係國際機<br />\n由於真係太平 我已經做好要delay嘅心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國際機唔洗入境，行李有得直掛爭好遠啦！<br />\n<br />\n我果次芬蘭入境，得行李可以直掛，落機過 security check 再 passport control , 仲要死關員所有香港人都問長問短，出示回租機票先俾入境。<br />\n<br />\n相都唔敢影張，電話卡香港買過去都冇時間 set ，到上咗機先安心。<br />\n<br />\n我去到閘口，check 完登機，就要我坐巴士出去上機。<br />\n<br />\n頭尾冇一個鐘，因為班芬航 delay 咗半個鐘，另外班機又早半個鐘登機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6649a73f07ac42132bfc25c264746eef3960bdd5","tid":131830,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"三國都唔大 <br />\n你鍾意day trip其實成個國家都去到<br />\n立陶宛巴打講左<br />\nLatvia可以去Jurmala, Rundale, Cesis, Sigulda, palanga, etc<br />\nEstonia可以去Tartu, Narva-joesuu, haapsalu, parnu<br />\n<br />\n以上有啲係自己去, 有啲聽人去過, daytrip hea遊曬太陽黎講唔錯<br />\n<br />\n仲有kaliningrad其實幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b406bc7e977abbed93cb20a4dbed8ab08bd7e3","tid":131830,"uid":81734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:47:23.000Z","msg":"波蘭嘢食好抵食！個個都話華沙悶但我幾鍾意，反而覺得krakow唔計集中營嗰啲，個城市好似香港無咩特色，可能我唔識玩啦<br />\n<br />\n華沙都有啲博物館可以行下，唔錯架"},{"pid":"7789d4b55a81a172ad004636c903ef7580322465","tid":131830,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:55:39.000Z","msg":"波蘭如果鍾意行山可以去zakopane"},{"pid":"2e5f3df6bea5167aa7162e47be26d073b1af315b","tid":131830,"uid":79185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波蘭如果鍾意行山可以去zakopane</blockquote><br />\n未打完就submit左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nestonia可以去saaremaa，有風車同隕石坑睇"},{"pid":"a236aba84e1e7e4e9e1db4a719dc8cd100830829","tid":131830,"uid":61052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"我就好鐘意krakow<br />\n坐响廣場飲下啤酒又一日"},{"pid":"701c5ee873b0a05987890db20f9736f313bd5e7b","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到咁多巴打去過波羅的海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bd5f703401fdfe1d1798c8fbf66e59fbb666bb","tid":131830,"uid":58081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間</blockquote><br />\n我早你地少少，5了月尾<br />\n到時可以約個地方食飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啊 獨遊撚最鐘意識朋友<br />\n不過我1/6先飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我22飛莫斯科<br />\n應該撞到既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb621c85017131729e7dbdd30ae6ef51e0e6be","tid":131830,"uid":35003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"9b6b7fe28139127a037faa334d1702c93df819f6","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:06:42.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d521b369c6de34e03bc49fd3c2448ba6d9f59fc8","tid":131830,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>估唔到咁多巴打去過波羅的海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n波羅的海，聖彼得堡，芬蘭，格但斯克呢啲全部都去過，不過係搭郵輪，所以幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ab37e566c3960a064f60ebdcb24027f48e86e5","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>估唔到咁多巴打去過波羅的海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n波羅的海，聖彼得堡，芬蘭，格但斯克呢啲全部都去過，不過係搭郵輪，所以幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要啊巴打 有冇景點值得推薦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18426e092afe40e6409ad192a906e76cef88600a","tid":131830,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>估唔到咁多巴打去過波羅的海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n波羅的海，聖彼得堡，芬蘭，格但斯克呢啲全部都去過，不過係搭郵輪，所以幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要啊巴打 有冇景點值得推薦啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全部係跟團玩。格但斯克，里加，塔林，赫爾辛基呢啲一日足夠。聖彼得堡就真係最起碼三日"},{"pid":"5f31c09b3a203980a29d76de063d5f7179511730","tid":131830,"uid":75475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:04:00.000Z","msg":"Baltic countries 記得坐 Lux Express <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大力推薦Sigulda"},{"pid":"8563b3b9caa5fd66e79502a4994c8e9cb69f2ef6","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:37:38.000Z","msg":"本身以為唔係熱門國家post好快沉 點知有咁多巴打俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望可以出遊記報答大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344d54b80906cef50663c2e460ea0dde09b4a293","tid":131830,"uid":78849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:43:23.000Z","msg":"既然去咁多日 巴打飛到華沙 之後落布拉格 維也納 再加布達佩斯都夠玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5841fa4a9732e66ecb35719071d9f050c6c5cd61","tid":131830,"uid":75475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:43:24.000Z","msg":"如果你去烏克蘭，除左去Kiev之外，Lviv都好值得去"},{"pid":"9a45abb4041a2dbe9cc43dbede63877bad2c566a","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>既然去咁多日 巴打飛到華沙 之後落布拉格 維也納 再加布達佩斯都夠玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好提議<br />\n不過上年年尾去左啦已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8989a46ee952203894d1f968afc729cc2bba817","tid":131830,"uid":78849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T18:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>既然去咁多日 巴打飛到華沙 之後落布拉格 維也納 再加布達佩斯都夠玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好提議<br />\n不過上年年尾去左啦已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係去過先介紹你 東歐真係超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有照原定路線 多啲時間係一個地方感受下睇多啲都好"},{"pid":"bc739ab3efa56a7dc8d47296dc5f952d1777b835","tid":131830,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T19:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身以為唔係熱門國家post好快沉 點知有咁多巴打俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望可以出遊記報答大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實講真，乜巴黎倫敦羅馬呢啲大家已經去到厭晒，又污糟又冇新意"},{"pid":"59dc7789a60a30957ce741fd1bcb8acf0f88916c","tid":131830,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你去烏克蘭，除左去Kiev之外，Lviv都好值得去</blockquote><br />\nLviv比較似波蘭，好似波蘭過去比較近"},{"pid":"a5478c1e797e5a5f0fb19d837b0fe41226741a93","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身以為唔係熱門國家post好快沉 點知有咁多巴打俾意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望可以出遊記報答大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n波羅的海三國都唔算好冷門啦！<br />\n<br />\n天氣就比香港冷"},{"pid":"3f319b1523051705cca059317c61239174d7904e","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你去烏克蘭，除左去Kiev之外，Lviv都好值得去</blockquote><br />\nLviv比較似波蘭，好似波蘭過去比較近</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有去 Gdansk 同埋 Krakow ，真係去 Lviv 會覺得差唔多，除咗消費更加平之外。"},{"pid":"cad002d7a20ea43a636cc096235edc0050344025","tid":131830,"uid":66540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"上年summer 去左波羅的海三國 <br />\n主要都係留係首都 <br />\ntallinn, riga, villulis平均一個地方留兩日 <br />\n再加多個trakai 一日遊 好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd3dc58948a1267cf4924326f8d58446218e51a","tid":131830,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T06:23:30.000Z","msg":"幫你推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月去波蘭烏克蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9e6f38f6d2fff868530491077ceef272308d70","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:20:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"657db3fd4e764707d55666af9df24da9dba08d40","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"270720442bfb59139a9afaf1e4f2bbf6559de348","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a52b9c346dc2465268e22dd49daeaa748432858c","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"02816dd1bcf9c27926af147abe8a4c5b70efdbc7","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:14:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"284ae05c4a743877bd603f64129e0cb3666a780d","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"84e442722aa638a0984569ccddce872fa9d75f71","tid":131830,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T06:31:05.000Z","msg":"華沙一日半咩都玩完悶到抽筋，krakow多啲玩好多"},{"pid":"b263dd083105b40d2a9a8cf6b5e9582ab0f158de","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"70827496b7f87c0ef979756e78c080ba0450ba3e","tid":131830,"uid":25474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都去咗<br />\nLithuania 完全唔需要去kaunas!!!千奇唔好去 去trakai仲好 不過我去唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有去到klaipeda 係海邊地方嚟 淨係去咗palanga無落nida <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悠閒hea一兩日幾舒服<br />\n<br />\nriga呢有個沙灘 j字頭嘅 市中心搭火車去好似一個鐘大概 勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己覺得warsaw無咩睇 krakow有集中營有意義好多 一定要去!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\ngdansk聽講都正 又係海邊嚟嘅(我比較鍾意去沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 但嗰陣巴士飛太貴最後無去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36d2ae2f4633a4278416d22b4816b7f02b4a47b","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都去咗<br />\nLithuania 完全唔需要去kaunas!!!千奇唔好去 去trakai仲好 不過我去唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有去到klaipeda 係海邊地方嚟 淨係去咗palanga無落nida <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悠閒hea一兩日幾舒服<br />\n<br />\nriga呢有個沙灘 j字頭嘅 市中心搭火車去好似一個鐘大概 勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gi