},{"pid":"eedfa4f51590c7c53b9ccc728f45b6cd56c68a99","tid":131830,"uid":55923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7月我都諗住波蘭-&gt;波羅的海-&gt;聖彼得堡-&gt;莫斯科番香港<br />\n<br />\n想問交通方唔方便?洗唔洗提早book定巴士?</blockquote><br />\n早book平一半  即日睇彩數"},{"pid":"dd74ceae387d66246815092de53966215b57e24f","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e902a1a8dba655564929d794690d9a37d7903dfd","tid":131830,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就好鐘意krakow<br />\n坐响廣場飲下啤酒又一日</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時行走Krakow, Katowice, 同埋我個波蘭女同學屋企<br />\n鄉下地方 好舒服 三九唔識七 同班鬼仔一齊踢波踢咗幾粒鐘 <br />\n一世何求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fac7cf55e7e17a41bfdf70bb875d5c3a84488b","tid":131830,"uid":25474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都去咗<br />\nLithuania 完全唔需要去kaunas!!!千奇唔好去 去trakai仲好 不過我去唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有去到klaipeda 係海邊地方嚟 淨係去咗palanga無落nida <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悠閒hea一兩日幾舒服<br />\n<br />\nriga呢有個沙灘 j字頭嘅 市中心搭火車去好似一個鐘大概 勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己覺得warsaw無咩睇 krakow有集中營有意義好多 一定要去!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\ngdansk聽講都正 又係海邊嚟嘅(我比較鍾意去沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 但嗰陣巴士飛太貴最後無去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心想知巴打點解對Kaunas咁大怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係絲打啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留過喺kaunas幾個禮拜<br />\n成個城市都好無聊完全無景點咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19689911f6fc1e3057602fdaf488039d61ff3f08","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ba3425acc8b36105373f27f0b92da26b14eee9ae","tid":131830,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T11:56:05.000Z","msg":"復活節去華沙karkow <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKarkow 會去鹽礦集中營<br />\n華沙未諗"},{"pid":"2fa5f050bfad20d865c144afb4bdd68f66710d0c","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"94374e51d190d160547b3c13a682b5b393278307","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0abbaf1bfb378b630db333d8e9bd0333e755d20d","tid":131830,"uid":31174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"華沙得啲 museum 兩日玩盡哂<br />\nkrakow就真係多好多野玩喇"},{"pid":"e62aa4a49d4bf73c5afd45c8bba4cfd1148580de","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c78b62320170a47bcb11c613851bc351916d3258","tid":131830,"uid":33752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"去埋zakopane 睇海洋之眼啦<br />\n波蘭好抵玩，啲野食平靚正"},{"pid":"133f5543bb4a3853bf4686ffd7de6845a894e04a","tid":131830,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都去咗<br />\nLithuania 完全唔需要去kaunas!!!千奇唔好去 去trakai仲好 不過我去唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有去到klaipeda 係海邊地方嚟 淨係去咗palanga無落nida <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悠閒hea一兩日幾舒服<br />\n<br />\nriga呢有個沙灘 j字頭嘅 市中心搭火車去好似一個鐘大概 勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己覺得warsaw無咩睇 krakow有集中營有意義好多 一定要去!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\ngdansk聽講都正 又係海邊嚟嘅(我比較鍾意去沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 但嗰陣巴士飛太貴最後無去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGdansk幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個沙灘啲囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋附近都多野行同食<br />\nHea翻兩日一流，不過價錢偏貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/194819_5b32dbec8811d8861ed95cabd5338db4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F194819_5b32dbec8811d8861ed95cabd5338db4.jpg&h=e53fdcff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"560b4b44957e42d98da36c63943f827fe8d943b4","tid":131830,"uid":88404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n計劃緊華沙入維也納出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052781454ffe11ac45dc7df7c1901827f08dbd6c","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9412374fdda7b5cf4a467383d836c5dcc5d1dd5f","tid":131830,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<br />\n計劃緊華沙入維也納出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同你調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1e2714165d27f50ffd850158a15122bce1653f","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:01:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e26fb5f80e6f495d889afc48d98dc2cdf875685f","tid":131830,"uid":45044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:38:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f077e98ae70fea2cded9d7113c560be7e369a253","tid":131830,"uid":4428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間</blockquote><br />\n我早你地少少，5了月尾<br />\n到時可以約個地方食飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啊 獨遊撚最鐘意識朋友<br />\n不過我1/6先飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry遲左覆<br />\n其實我未諗好 因為7月-8月一個月去summer exchange<br />\n所以未諗好exchange前去定後去好<br />\n前就6月中開始 後去就8月頭開始"},{"pid":"fd68061475747c6c36ff1b6a7c5564c778a9fbbf","tid":131830,"uid":4428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都去咗<br />\nLithuania 完全唔需要去kaunas!!!千奇唔好去 去trakai仲好 不過我去唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有去到klaipeda 係海邊地方嚟 淨係去咗palanga無落nida <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 悠閒hea一兩日幾舒服<br />\n<br />\nriga呢有個沙灘 j字頭嘅 市中心搭火車去好似一個鐘大概 勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己覺得warsaw無咩睇 krakow有集中營有意義好多 一定要去!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\ngdansk聽講都正 又係海邊嚟嘅(我比較鍾意去沙灘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 但嗰陣巴士飛太貴最後無去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGdansk幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個沙灘啲囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋附近都多野行同食<br />\nHea翻兩日一流，不過價錢偏貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/01/194819_5b32dbec8811d8861ed95cabd5338db4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2F194819_5b32dbec8811d8861ed95cabd5338db4.jpg&h=e53fdcff&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波蘭除左 warsaw同埋krakow仲有冇啲咩地方值得去"},{"pid":"24255f826eeb314445e5235cbe0c2eb6624594d2","tid":131830,"uid":4428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>LM學野 我都係咁上下時間去東歐</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇schedule？睇下撞唔撞時間</blockquote><br />\n我早你地少少，5了月尾<br />\n到時可以約個地方食飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啊 獨遊撚最鐘意識朋友<br />\n不過我1/6先飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry遲左覆<br />\n其實我未諗好 因為7月-8月一個月去summer exchange<br />\n所以未諗好exchange前去定後去好<br />\n前就6月中開始 後去就8月頭開始</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就諗住由北歐玩落東歐<br />\n因為我係北歐exchange<br />\n首先係北歐落波蘿的海三國啦<br />\n之後玩埋balkans<br />\n最後因為真係太想去波蘭睇集中營所以會去埋<br />\n仲有錢淨會去埋德國（但我諗都應該冇了）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f7475ca1773a07bbc944df208b0c8a10c1b629","tid":131830,"uid":74547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"6月中由匈牙利玩到俄羅斯<br />\n想問下有無人知波蘭過境烏克蘭麻唔麻煩?"},{"pid":"d51ef8a5d9c90cc