nGdansk"},{"pid":"f72d7668aec57ef15b46a7c9242d4893d3a40219","tid":131830,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>6月中由匈牙利玩到俄羅斯<br />\n想問下有無人知波蘭過境烏克蘭麻唔麻煩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本passport仲要有俄羅斯visa, 會5會俾人留難/唔俾入境?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會。<br />\n<br />\n我個PASSPORT 10次出入境俄羅斯印，都照入兩次烏克蘭。"},{"pid":"a1680b9b3b4683539939770b016ccb7bd02ffa58","tid":131830,"uid":8414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:40:45.000Z","msg":"去過warsaw vilnius trakai kaunas palanga riga sigulda parnu tallinn tartu<br />\n順住咁去<br />\nkaunas真係唔駛去，成個城市都無景點睇好似返左大陸咁<br />\nparnu tartu 其實都無咩野睇，無時間唔駛特登去<br />\nwarsaw個古城係摧毀完重建，都好一般，依家好後悔無去krakow<br />\nsigulda當時去歐洲已經去到審美疲勞，所以無去睇城堡，反而去左adventure park玩繩索同飛索，計落平過係香港玩，本身滿心期待去住森林小屋，點知去到先知原來係人地後欄嘅小屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019f008f9e7e9042e74678733fa045f74984ab2b","tid":131830,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n <br />\nThx巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我plan行程預左一日去明斯克 希望快d實施免簽<br />\n<br />\n講起白俄 話說我上入境處個網睇話要簽證 跟手打去問 諗住佢有d最新資訊 點知佢自己都係上返果個網睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三國中，以立陶宛最多嘢睇，可以去四個城市，除 Vilnius 外， Kaunas, Trakai 城堡，&Scaron;iauliai 十字架山，Klaipėda Nida 沙嘴。<br />\n<br />\n去拉脱維亞里加可以去埋 Sigulda 城堡。<br />\n<br />\n塔林同聖彼德堡的愛俄邊界，都有城堡 Narva。<br />\n<br />\n不過同波蘭比，波蘭 Malbork 秒殺好多個。<br />\n<br />\n我都等梗白俄免簽，不過暫時機票唔算平，唔急買住！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年都去咗<br />\nLithuani